## 4. Repo fit

```text
docs/                         ← human-facing control plane (Directory Rules §6.1)
└── brand/                    ← styles guides, logo, voice (PROPOSED canonical home)
    └── logo/
        └── print/            ← THIS FOLDER — print-distribution wordmark assets
```

**Upstream** *(PROPOSED)*

- Brand-design source files (vector source, e.g. `.ai` / `.sketch` / `.fig`) — home **UNKNOWN** in this session; likely not under `docs/brand/` per the docs/ no-binary-source convention. Candidate homes: `data/raw/brand/` or an external design system. **NEEDS VERIFICATION.**
- Brand color, typography, and voice specifications — likely siblings under `docs/brand/` (`docs/brand/colors.md`, `docs/brand/typography.md`, `docs/brand/voice.md`). **NEEDS VERIFICATION.**

**Downstream** *(PROPOSED)*

- Cover pages and front-matter for KFM PDF dossiers built under the C13 reproducible-PDF chain.
- Print stationery, exhibit panels, conference materials, signage.
- Catalog and registry entries that cite the wordmark by `artifact_digest`.

---

## 5. What belongs here

Accepted contents of `docs/brand/logo/print/`:

| File / pattern | Role | Required? |
|---|---|---|
| `kfm-wordmark-print.pdf` | Primary print-ready vector wordmark | **Yes** |
| `kfm-wordmark-print.pdf.sidecar.json` | Sidecar manifest: `spec_hash`, `artifact_digest`, color profile, output intent, font-embed status, conformance level | **Yes** *(PROPOSED — aligns with C13-04)* |
| `kfm-wordmark-print.license.md` | License + attribution + permitted-use declaration | **Yes** *(PROPOSED — aligns with ML-F-002 / ML-F-004)* |
| `kfm-wordmark-print-*.pdf` (variants) | Single-color, reversed, monochrome variants — each with its own sidecar + license | Optional |
| `CHANGELOG.md` | Asset-level version history with rotation reasons and supersession chain | Recommended |
| `README.md` (this file) | Folder governance | **Yes** |

---

## 6. What does *not* belong here

| Do **not** put here | Belongs in |
|---|---|
| Vector design sources (`.ai`, `.sketch`, `.fig`) | `data/raw/brand/` *(PROPOSED)* or external design system |
| Web-optimized wordmarks (`.svg`, `.png`, web `.pdf`) | A sibling `docs/brand/logo/digital/` *(PROPOSED)* — different distribution profile |
| MapLibre sprites, glyphs, symbol sheets | `packages/maplibre/` or canonical sprite home *(PROPOSED)* |
| UI logo components / React assets | `packages/ui/` *(per Directory Rules)* |
| Receipts, proofs, release manifests | `data/receipts/`, `data/proofs/`, `release/` — never here, per Directory Rules §8.2 |
| Personal mock-ups, exploratory drafts | `docs/archive/exploratory/` |
| Compiled marketing decks, slide exports | `artifacts/docs/` if generated; `docs/` if hand-authored governance prose |

> [!CAUTION]
> The `artifacts/` root MUST NOT be used as a parallel home for the wordmark or its sidecar manifest. Trust-bearing material is governed under `docs/`, `release/`, and `data/` per Directory Rules §8.2.

