## 14. Review burden

| Role | Responsibility |
|---|---|
| Brand stewards *(PROPOSED CODEOWNERS pattern: `@org/brand-stewards`)* | Approve any change to `kfm-wordmark-print.pdf`, its sidecar, or its license |
| Documentation maintainers | Review README and convention drift |
| Release authority | Required co-sign when the wordmark is rotated and downstream artifacts must be reissued |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> A wordmark rotation is a **release-class change**. It changes the `artifact_digest` of every downstream PDF that embeds it, which means every citing receipt becomes stale. Treat rotations like a schema-home migration: ADR, supersession entry, correction notices to affected published artifacts.

